Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.52,0:00:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This girl is Kouyama Mitsuki. 12 years old!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.73,0:00:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The recording day for her debut song, "Myself", had come...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:06.31,0:00:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And then that Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.68,0:00:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He fell asleep while he was a stuffed animal, and some strange girl picked him up.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's because he's such an oaf.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki managed to get him back, though.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Her recording went off without a hitch.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll keep this a secret from the chief, 'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?{missing line}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.20,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}Well then.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}We still have another song for you!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.09,0:00:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}In just a moment... we'll have the song that all eyes are on this week.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}Isn't it amazing? Here it is...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}...on sale this week... the song, "Myself".
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.71,0:00:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}This song is actually...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}...from the artist who made Seed Records' New Artist audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.81,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}...in just one try... the debut song for {\i1}Full Moon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.11,0:00:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}...is produced by Takasu Kohei.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.44,0:00:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.97,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can you please turn off the radio?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I detest music.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.77,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}However, Takasu-san was unable to join us for an interview during this break.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.78,0:00:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}Which brings us to the song that's caught everyone's attention!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}Listen to this.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85\i1}Full Moon's...{\i0}
