Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is your first live concert, isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where are you performing?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.69,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where, indeed...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're so helpless.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll go look for it.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where did your manager say it was...?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That...she didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.80,0:02:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}"I'll know when I reach the center."
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, where exactly is this "center"?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.43,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Shani,{Nande? When it's so easy too?}
