Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\bord\shad0\pos(254.898,159)\frz339.1}{\c&H3C2A2F&}bu
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\bord\shad0\frz329.9\pos(282.942,172)}{\c&H3C2A2F&}ya
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\bord\shad0\frz322.6\pos(341.033,206)}{\c&H3C2A2F&}Ce
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\bord\shad0\frz316.2\pos(362.065,224)}{\c&H3C2A2F&}nt
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\bord\shad0\pos(380.094,244)\frz307.8}{\c&H3C2A2F&}er
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\bord\shad0\frz297.3\pos(416.65,302)}{\c&H3C2A2F&}Str
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.45,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\bord\shad0\frz286.5\pos(430.173,335)}{\c&H3C2A2F&}eet
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.67,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man, you're such a hick? {Hick: Unsophisticated, simpleton, country bumpkin = Pointless, Stupid Note, not as bad as keikaku though}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's because this is my first time in Shibuya!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, where exactly are we?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.02,0:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why are they all looking up?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.62,0:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.95,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who is that?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's that girl.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know, the one who was \Nchosen at that audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.53,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{BAD FRAME}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I know her.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I heard her song on the radio.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... that girl, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's really cute.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They said you're cute.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How does the {\i1}object of worship{\i0}  feel about it?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.72,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.96,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why...?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.67,0:03:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For some reason... that doesn't look like me...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You could say...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that there's a gap between what's real and what's just an image.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}Please line up over here!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}Today is Full Moon's special live concert.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}Those who wish to enjoy it...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}...please line up over here.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's this many people gathered for a new artist who hasn't even debuted, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In-Incredible.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to sing in front of this many people... {merged lines for better phrasing}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}C-Can I sing well, I wonder?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What if I get the words wrong..?{question mark}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When that happens...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}"When that happens..."{\i0}{italic and quotation}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Smile and make it up! {Protip}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want to do that!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I worked so hard to come up with those lyrics.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So you won't get them wrong, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm worried I can do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Now is not the time to \Nstart thinking like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.56,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have to find somewhere to transform you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's see... The exit is...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're {\i1}Full Moon,{\i0} aren't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't you remember me? {Mitsuki doesn't remember sore losers}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.16,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At the beginning of the audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't remember?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... sorry. {but I don't remember losers}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... was the one after you. {LOL, YOU HAD NO SHOT BECAUSE MITSUKI PWNED EVERYONE}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was Number 22 at the audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks to you...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I had to go home without auditioning. {Oh boo-hoo *plays the world's smallest violin}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Today's audition is over. {Damn straight}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.12,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The previously expected third judging will not take place.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.36,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.57,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back then...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's not something you need to apologize for.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.00,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If someone gets chosen...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...everyone else is disappointed.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because I...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...don't think that I would have lost to you. {GET THE F OUTTA HERE XD}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.92,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I had gone instead of you...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I would have been the one chosen instead. {Coulda, woulda, shoulda}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I suppose that could have happened...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.01,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm an incredible singer. {Translation: I'm a talentless hack}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good to see she doesn't lack self-confidence.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.00,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's so beneficial...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that cuteness of yours.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.10,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You didn't know?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You weren't chosen for you singing...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The decision was based solely on your looks. {Shani: Then they did great! Mitsuki is so damn cute!}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.40,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it wasn't for that, there's no way you would have been selected...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.04,0:06:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...with such a mediocre song.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Today's concert...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can do all sorts of tricks with the mic for your CD, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.67,0:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you can't do something\N like that for a live concert.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}With only your looks...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Having to sing in front of flocks of people...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.97,0:06:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'd be best if you realized your position as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's such a spiteful girl. {What a spiteful *will end it there}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.06,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.98,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was chosen for my looks...?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.90,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Not for my voice...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.90,Notice,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\org(454,139)\frx14\fry338\pos(56.001,65)\frz20.69}Full Moon-sama {Needs Fine-tuning}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.90,Notice,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\frx12\fry338\frz17.72\pos(54.981,299.6)\org(460,327)}Waiting Room {Needs Fine-tuning}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't she late?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe she got the place wrong...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.07,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's arrived.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. She's here! She's here!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look! Look!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't that a great poster?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I saw it.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's the first time you've seen yourself like that, isn't it? {a.f.k forgot it after isn't, fixed}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was Takasu-san's idea \Nto go all-out and be flashy.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.99,0:07:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.69,0:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}N-No...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've been through this before, too...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When you were an idol, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right. {Bad memories written on her face}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The first stage I debuted on...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...was at a poolside in an amusement park, though.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Right in font of the stage, I was frozen stiff with nervousness.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After the other idols saw that, they taught me...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.73,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}..at times like this...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...in the palm of your hand...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.50,Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(42,0)}(Hitto: A Hit)
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Write {\i1}hitto.{\i0} {Can't realy do anything with this one}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, you take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you do that, you won't get nervous.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's wrong, Ooshige-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.80,Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(42,0)}(Hito: Person)
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Not {\i1}hitto{\i0}, it's {\i1}hito.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hito as in humans.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... then... I didn't make it because of that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! I was tricked! Damn it!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Give me back my youth!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Give it back!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.23,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Give it back!!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.81,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Give it back!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.48,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't think that was why you didn't make it.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki, be sure to write {\i1}hito{\i0}  properly.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}O-Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.95,0:08:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.32,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Was I chosen at the audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...because I look cute?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who told you that?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who...? Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My ears seem to be failing me.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can you say that again?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't matter how well I sing...?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course it matters.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't know who told you this, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you made the audition, and today's...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... you should get ready soon...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's almost time.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.00,0:09:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's all in your hands now, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.74,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just focus on the live concert right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... s-sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come over here, then. {this is one of the make-up ladies calling Mitsuki}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh... me too.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow! It's crazy outside!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.73,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There are lines all the way down the street.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll have to do a perfect job here.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.55,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... wonder if I'll be able to sing.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.88,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where is she?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The bathroom.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.87,0:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.85,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you want to eat this?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a new potato product.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm. It looks good.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}With only your looks...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Having to sing in front of flocks of people...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.01,0:11:10.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'd be best if you realized your position as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So you were up here, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto... I...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.47,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.68,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My hair's all messed up!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're so mean!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And they just made me look pretty...!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmph!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A singer who only depends on looks...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.22,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course you're concerned about your appearance, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.27,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have I said too much?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Should I beg for forgiveness, too?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.40,0:11:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The birth of the industry's first idol in disguise...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you've become the topic of \Ndiscussion everywhere.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmph!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you running away?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sing like you're supposed to.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to sing.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because that's my job.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.20,0:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.21,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who do you think you are, \Nsaying it's just a job!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter how hard it gets...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you're going to smile and do your best, because it's your job?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't say anything like that!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\i1}"Because it's my job..."{\i0}{Quotation}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you're going to have such \Na cold attitude about it...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you won't be able to \Ntouch anyone's heart.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.39,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You need to enjoy singing \Nfrom the heart first.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.27,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Right now, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I haven't mentioned it before, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When you auditioned...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back then, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...was surprised and moved.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.12,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You sang with such a beautiful voice.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Somehow, it didn't seem like a voice...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...more like an aura of sound.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even the lower tones came through clearly.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was like a dream.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That such a singer existed...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.69,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I was overjoyed.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back then...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I was happy, too!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's been so long since \NI'd sung in such a loud voice...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Breathing didn't hurt either.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It may seem normal to most people, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...to be able to use that kind of voice...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...makes me very happy!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Singing... is all about expressing \Nyour feelings, isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I sing without confidence...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that's what the people \Nwho are listening will hear.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, still... I...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.59,0:13:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay! I'm going!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over there. Look at that!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.94,0:14:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.20,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A huge mountain of postcards...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}These are all advance orders sent to this store for your CD.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.26,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It seems like a lot, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...these are just the orders from this store.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Full Moon's Debut Single...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I am placing an advanced order for "Myself".
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Please fulfill my request.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}I heard it on the radio...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}and loved it after just one listen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}It's a really great song, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}It's the best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}I wonder what the girl who sang it is like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}I'm very interested.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}She's a young girl, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}...she has a pleasing voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}It cleanses the soul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.25,0:14:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This was the response to your publicity single that's airing on the radio.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.67,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You weren't just "chosen for your looks."
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You believe me, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.09,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.09,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Becoming strong...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.72,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...is hard, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.93,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But for now...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.06,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll keep walking forward.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.89,0:15:19.52,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Surely...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.98,0:15:20.90,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.02,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...not alone.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,435)}Takasu-san! {exclamatory added}
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,435)}What a trick you've set up!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That was an amazing display.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-chan sure knows what she's doing...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was wonderful, Takasu-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was really wonderful, Ooshige-chan!{timing fix: start}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just felt that I should do something for her.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've lost.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.21,0:18:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm no match for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your singing was too good.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It only makes sense that you were chosen.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.18,0:18:41.60,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh...?{Internal thought}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Which is why...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...for saying all that...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm really sorry. {Bow to the master}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.11,0:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have faith in my singing, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'm going to work even harder!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Me, too...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.94,0:19:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In order to share my \Nfeelings with everyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I have to work hard!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have to both work hard, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're right.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You really were here.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It wasn't much... just some \Nfeathers floating around.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Not that...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.14,0:19:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What you told me earlier...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You were trying to cheer me up, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.98,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just can't stand people who \Nhesitate and constantly worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.24,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In the end... you got them across...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...your feelings, right?{replaced "yeah" with "right"}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:34.85,0:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That girl's song...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a huge hit!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The kids at school are probably...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...all talking about {\i1}Full Moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even the manager said it was a great hit.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.03,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nobody's talking about {\i1}Full Moon,{\i0} huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:46.87,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If nobody's heard of her...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll let them all know!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.74,0:21:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait, Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.98,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you go out, you'll let something slip again!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
